stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Chemotherapy (CTX)<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c991400 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c991400\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b748f33\" data-id=\"b748f33\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e878a96 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e878a96\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<strong>Definition<\/strong>\n<ul>\n \t<li>Definition: Chemical Medications Used to Kill Rapidly-Growing Cells<\/li>\n \t<li>Inhibits Mitosis or Induces DNA Damage<\/li>\n \t<li>Often Many Drugs are Used Together as a Regimen\n<ul>\n \t<li>Ex: FOLFOX in Colon Cancer (Folinic Acid, 5-FU &amp; Oxaliplatin)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n \t<li>Side Effects <a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #193556; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 2px;\" href=\"#MN\">Mn <\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<strong>Chemotherapy Classification<\/strong>\n<ul>\n \t<li>Alkylating Agents \u2013 Inhibit DNA Replication by Creating an Unstable Alkyl Group<\/li>\n \t<li>Antimetabolites \u2013 Inhibits DNA Replication<\/li>\n \t<li>Antimicrotubular Agents<\/li>\n \t<li>Others:\n<ul>\n \t<li>Antibiotics<\/li>\n \t<li>Enzymes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<strong>Chemoprotective Agents<\/strong>\n<ul>\n \t<li>Definition: Drugs Used to Moderate the Side Effects of Chemotherapy Treatments<\/li>\n \t<li><em>Leucovorin (<strong>Folinic Acid<\/strong>)<\/em>\n<ul>\n \t<li>Use: Reverse Side Effects of <strong>Methotrexate<\/strong> (\u201cRescue Therapy\u201d)<\/li>\n \t<li>Side Effects: Worsens Toxicity of 5-FU<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n \t<li>Amifostine\n<ul>\n \t<li>Use: Prevents Nephrotoxicity from Cisplatin &amp; Carboplatin<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n \t<li>Mesna\n<ul>\n \t<li>Use: Prevents Hemorrhagic Cystitis from Cyclophosphamide<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n \t<li>Dexrazoxane\n<ul>\n \t<li>Use: Prevents Cardiotoxicity from Doxorubicin<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n \t<li><em>Granulocyte Colony-Stimulating Factor (GCSF\/Neupogen\/Granix)<\/em>\n<ul>\n \t<li>Use: Neutrophil Recovery After Chemotherapy<\/li>\n \t<li>Side Effects: <em>Sweet\u2019s Syndrome<\/em> \u2013 Acute Febrile Neutropenic Dermatitis<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ebe662d elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ebe662d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-01a427b\" data-id=\"01a427b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a671c94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a671c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Chemotherapy Agents<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4154636 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4154636\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-93661ba\" data-id=\"93661ba\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83e39d8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"83e39d8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Alkylating Agents<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Alkyl Sulfonates:<ul><li><em>Busulfan<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: <strong>Pulmonary Fibrosis<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Nitrogen Mustards:<ul><li><em>Cyclophosphamide<\/em><ul><li>Binds Cyclophilin &amp; <strong>Inhibits Calcineurin<\/strong><\/li><li>Side Effects: Gonad Dysfunction, SIADH &amp; <strong>Hemorrhagic Cystitis<\/strong> (Tx: Mesna)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Ifosfamide<\/em><\/li><li><em>Bendamustine<\/em><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Nitrosoureas:<ul><li><em>Carmustine<\/em><\/li><li><em>Lomustine<\/em><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Platinum Analogs:<ul><li><em>Carboplatin<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: Myelosuppression<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Cisplatin<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: Nephrotoxic, Neurotoxic &amp; Ototoxic<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Oxaliplatin<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: Peripheral Neuropathy<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Triazanes:<ul><li><em>Dacarbazine<\/em><\/li><li><em>Procarbazine<\/em><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Antimetabolites<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Cytidine Analogs:<ul><li><em>Gemcitabine<\/em><\/li><li><em>Azacytidine<\/em><\/li><li><em>Decitabine<\/em><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Folate Antagonists (Dihydrofolate Reductase Inhibitor):<ul><li><em>Methotrexate (MTX)<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: Myelosuppression &amp; Nephrotoxicity<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Purine Analogs:<ul><li><em>Cladribine<\/em><\/li><li><em>Clofarabine<\/em><\/li><li><em>Nelarabine<\/em><\/li><li><em>Mercaptopurine (6-MP)<\/em><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Pyrimidine Analogs:<ul><li><em>Fluorouracil (5-FU)<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: Myelosuppression<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Capecitabine (Oral 5-FU)<\/em><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Antimicrotubular Agents<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Taxanes:<ul><li><em>Pacitaxel<\/em><\/li><li><em>Docetaxel<\/em><\/li><li><em>Cabazitaxel<\/em><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Topoisomerase I Inhibitors:<ul><li><em>Irinotecan<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: Diarrhea, N\/V &amp; Neutropenia<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Topotecan<\/em><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Topoisomerase II Inhibitors:<ul><li><em>Doxorubicin<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: <strong>Cardiotoxicity<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Idarubicin<\/em><\/li><li><em>Etoposide<\/em><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Vinca Alkaloids<ul><li><em>Vinblastine<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: Myelosuppression<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Vincristine<\/em><ul><li>Side Effects: <strong>Peripheral Neuropathy<\/strong> &amp; Neurotoxic<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Other Agents<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Bleomycin<ul><li>Mechanism: Antibiotic Also Inhibits DNA Synthesis<\/li><li>Side Effects: <strong>Pulmonary Fibrosis<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Hydroxyurea<ul><li>Mechanism: Inhibits Ribonucleoside Diphosphate Reductase<\/li><li>Side Effects: Myelosuppression<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Tretinoin<ul><li>Mechanism: Vitamin A Derivative Also Targets RAR-Alpha<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3b185a3 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3b185a3\" data-element_